2023 🍻 What a year it’s been!  I never expected I’d be as busy as I’ve been since retiring from racing. Between @trolltraining continuing to grow, learning the ropes of the family business @scmxpark building a house, training for marathons and becoming a dad, it’s been a bit crazy. But I’m grateful for it all and excited for what’s in store for 2024! ❤️🙌
